       exe-exp-ost-750.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo a Next su [ost]                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-ost-200.
       exe-exp-ost-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Close files                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
